page.title: 03 WILDLIFE,CHILBOROHILL FARM
page.content: IN THE ACRES OF LAND OF CHILBOROHILL FARM THERE IS LOTS OF WILDLIFE.THESE ARE SOME OF THE WATER BIRDS;MOOR HENS, HERONS, CANADA GEESE,THE DUCKS KICK THEIR YOUNG INTO THE WATER WHEN THEY ARE BORN AND A KINGFISHER,A RARE SIGHT. THESE ARE THE OTHER BIRDS;COOTS,COLLAR- DOVES,PIGEONS,CROWS ,THE ROOKS HAVE A FUNNY HABIT,THEY STAND ON THE FENCE AND FALL INTO THE CORN.A BARN OWL NESTS IN THEIR HUGE BARN. IN THE WOOD THERE ARE;SQUIRRELS,A GREEN WOODPECKER,AND A VERY RARE BARKING DEER.THERE ARE LOTS OF OTHER ANIMALS AND BIRDS LIVING IN CHILBOROHILL FARM.
